25:28.166 --> 25:29.600
Health class?

25:29.634 --> 25:32.503
Oh, thank God.

25:32.537 --> 25:33.771
[Sighs]

25:33.805 --> 25:36.173
So, you and Noel...

25:36.208 --> 25:39.432
Mom, stop it. We're friends.

25:39.811 --> 25:41.545
We haven't kissed or anything.

25:41.580 --> 25:43.681
So, are you a couple?

25:43.715 --> 25:46.890
Our generation doesn't really
put labels on things.

25:49.821 --> 25:52.656
I do hope that you'll
wait until you're older.

25:52.691 --> 25:54.491
It's a big deal.

25:54.526 --> 25:56.493
And I don't want you to end up
regretting something.

25:56.528 --> 26:00.798
Because some boys,
they will say anything,

26:00.832 --> 26:02.633
