as you heard what I had to say.

26:16.381 --> 26:18.415
- I did. I promise.
- [Sighs]

26:18.450 --> 26:21.419
You know you can talk
to me about anything.

26:26.884 --> 26:28.993
[Vivian cries]
Okay, shh, shh, shh, shh, shh.

26:29.027 --> 26:31.262
[Door opens]

26:31.296 --> 26:33.731
What's going on?
Is she still not better?

26:33.765 --> 26:35.699
Like I said in my text,
the thermometer says she's fine,

26:35.734 --> 26:38.202
but she feels really warm.

26:39.435 --> 26:40.718
She's burning up.

26:40.738 --> 26:42.606
- Do you want me to page her pediatrician?
- Don't bother.

26:42.641 --> 26:45.072
He'll just tell us to
meet him in the E.R.,

26:45.092 --> 26:46.577
which is where I'm taking her right now.

26:46.611 --> 26:49.580
All right, sweetie.
All right, sweetie. I got you.

26:49.614 --> 26:51.415
- Here.
- It's okay, sweetie.

26:51.449 --> 26:54.018
Oh, baby.

26:54.052 --> 26:56.320
Okay. Thank you.

26:58.290 --> 27:00.724
Joss.

27:00.759 --> 27:03.193
- Thank you so much for coming in.
- Mm-hmm. Happy to.

27:03.228 --> 27:04.862
You know, Harry's important to me,

27:04.896 --> 27:07.264
and I just want to make
this right for him, so...

27:07.299 --> 27:08.632
And I'm sure we all can agree

27:08.667 --> 27:11.735
that this was a misunderstanding.

27:16.241 --> 27:17.741
Um, I'm sorry.

27:20.779 --> 27:22.446
That's your apology?

27:22.480 --> 27:24.230
After what you did to me?

27:24.476 --> 27:27.418
You have a broken elbow, okay? Chill
out. It could have been much worse.

27:27.452 --> 27:30.241
Okay, you get your little power play.
What more do you want from me?

27:30.261 --> 27:32.323
I want to know that you mean it.

27:32.357 --> 27:33.957
I want you to beg for my forgiveness.

27:33.992 --> 27:37.588
Okay, you can stop right now
because that's not happening.

27:37.608 --> 27:39.797
You know, I'm... I'm so sorry, Jonathan.

27:39.831 --> 27:40.864
You think you're the good guy here,

27:40.899 --> 27:42.834
but you should know
that your nephew is the one

27:42.854 --> 27:44.668
who belongs in jail, which is
where he's gonna end up soon,

27:44.703 --> 27:46.768
given the coddling that's
happening in this family.

27:46.788 --> 27:48.639
- Excuse me?
- And that's the best-case scenario.

27:48.673 --> 27:50.674
Worse case scenario is
that this spoiled kid

27:50.709 --> 27:52.176
hurts or kills someone else.

27:52.210 --> 27:53.677
You know, I should have
taken care of you

27:53.712 --> 27:55.112
