29:14.154 --> 29:15.544
Hey.

29:17.232 --> 29:19.481
So, um, I just saw Reza.

29:19.501 --> 29:20.640
Again.

29:20.660 --> 29:22.561
I went to apologize.

29:22.595 --> 29:25.530
You did? Okay. Great.

29:25.565 --> 29:27.866
How'd it go?

29:27.900 --> 29:29.234
Well...

29:29.268 --> 29:30.902
Well?

29:30.937 --> 29:33.839
No. Um... not well.

29:33.873 --> 29:36.917
You know, Harry, I-I tried.
Really, I did.

29:36.937 --> 29:39.239
