29:39.273 --> 29:40.406
Now he's gonna press charges?

29:40.441 --> 29:42.542
- I don't know. Maybe.
- Joss...

29:42.576 --> 29:44.210
You know, they probably
won't do anything anyway.

29:44.245 --> 29:45.211
It would just be bad press for them.

29:45.246 --> 29:47.180
