29:58.359 --> 30:00.493
Why would you want to work
with someone like that?

30:00.527 --> 30:01.594
Jonathan loves his family.

30:01.629 --> 30:03.029
That doesn't make him a slimeball.

30:03.063 --> 30:04.530
In fact, he's trying
to help the situation.

30:04.565 --> 30:05.999
