30:06.033 --> 30:08.201
to risk my entire career, Joss.

30:09.303 --> 30:11.371
Uh, wow.

30:11.405 --> 30:13.339
I'm sorry, Harry.

30:13.374 --> 30:15.467
I didn't mean to do that.

30:16.577 --> 30:19.078
Where is all this rage
coming from, Joss?

30:19.113 --> 30:20.880
[Sighs]

30:20.915 --> 30:22.682
Hey.

30:22.716 --> 30:23.850
Can we talk about it?

30:23.884 --> 30:25.905
[Gasps] No, you know what, Harry?
I'm just... I'm really...

30:25.925 --> 30:29.134
I think I'm all talked out
for the moment.

30:31.558 --> 30:33.059
It's not whooping cough.

30:33.093 --> 30:34.427
So it's pneumonia?

30:34.461 --> 30:36.930
A moderate case.
I have some amoxicillin on hand.

30:36.950 --> 30:38.731
I'm gonna give her 350 milligrams.

30:38.766 --> 30:40.633
- Sound good?
- Yeah.

30:40.668 --> 30:41.901
Perfect.

30:41.936 --> 30:43.636
Okay.

30:43.671 --> 30:46.472
We will be back.

30:46.507 --> 30:49.375
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

30:54.682 --> 30:58.318
I can't imagine how hard
it was for you, coming here.

30:58.352 --> 30:59.619
