30:59.653 --> 31:01.487
I owe you an apology.

31:01.522 --> 31:04.457
I'm the one who started all of this,
and you didn't deserve that.

31:04.491 --> 31:07.226
And I didn't mean all those
things that I said. I just...

31:07.261 --> 31:10.430
I got caught up in the moment.

31:10.464 --> 31:12.932
So I'm sorry.

31:12.967 --> 31:15.301
I appreciate that.

31:15.336 --> 31:18.237
